Template: nnm-control/domain
Type: string
Default: nimble.example.com
Description: Panel domain:
 The domain name the panel will be served on. A DNS A-record for this
 domain must point to this machine's IP address.

Template: nnm-control/port
Type: string
Default: 8090
Description: Panel port:
 The TCP port on this machine the panel will listen on.
